data.description: Looking for new owner to enjoy and love this recently updated home featuring new paint, new carpet, spacious family room, large kitchen with solid surface countertops, SS appliances, and new LVP floors and cabinets overlooking a dining area featuring real hardwood flooring. Use the sliding door to access the covered deck and large back yard, which is perfect for relaxing or entertaining family and friends. The 2nd floor boasts a full bath, 2 spacious bedrooms and a primary bedroom with its own private ensuite.  Start your day relaxing with your morning coffee under the covered front porch. This home is a must see.
